# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [1.3.1] 2024-05-31

### Changed

- onChange callback when called from onConnect, now takes the initial value as the previous parameter

## [1.3.0] 2024-05-30

### Changed

- onChange callback now has access to the previous context's value

## [1.2.1] 2023-04-20

### Updated

- Updated license copyright to be in line with SaaSquatch open-source policy

## [1.2.0] 2021-03-31

### Changed

- #1 Context events are now `composed` and cross through shadow dom

### Fixed

- #2 Listeners stop if not connected

## [1.0.1] - 2021-01-12

### Changed

- Initial release

## [1.0.0] - 2021-01-12

### Added

- Initial release

